msgid ""
"Static remapping via `command line arguments <../How-To-Guides/Node-"
"arguments>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/Releases/Release-Bouncy-Bolson.rst:125
msgid "Various improvements to the Python client library."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/Releases/Release-Bouncy-Bolson.rst:126
